data.description: This stunning home has undergone several impressive upgrades and renovations. The driveway has been widened with proper permits, providing easier access to the rear of the property. The deck has been reinforced and inspected, ensuring safety and durability. The garage now features electric and insulation, making it a versatile and comfortable space. For pet owners, the invisible fence has been installed and will remain. Inside, the kitchen has been beautifully opened, featuring elegant granite countertops. The addition of recessed lighting and pendant lighting creates a warm and inviting atmosphere. A new chandelier adds a touch of sophistication to the space. The electrical panel has been replaced with a new one, ensuring optimal functionality and safety. The lower level boasts new flooring, adding a fresh and modern touch. The washer and dryer are included, making laundry a breeze. Additionally, the detached garage is equipped with a 240-volt sub-panel with 125 amps, providing ample power for any projects or hobbies. With a remodeled kitchen and an open floor plan, this home is perfect for entertaining and everyday living. Lastly, the bamboo flooring throughout adds a touch of natural beauty and durability.  ASSUMPTION IS PERMITTED
